snippet.title: Superman | Sneak Peek
snippet.description:
Krypto, take us home. #Superman - Only in Theaters July 11

‚ÄúSuperman,‚Äù DC Studios‚Äô first feature film to hit the big screen, is set to soar into theaters worldwide this summer from Warner Bros. Pictures.  In his signature style, James Gunn takes on the original superhero in the newly imagined DC universe with a singular blend of epic action, humor and heart, delivering a Superman who‚Äôs driven by compassion and an inherent belief in the goodness of humankind.

DC Studios heads Peter Safran and Gunn are producing the film, which Gunn directs from his own screenplay, based on characters from DC, Superman created by Jerry Siegel and Joe Shuster.

The film stars David Corenswet (‚ÄúTwisters,‚Äù ‚ÄúHollywood‚Äù) in the dual role of Superman/Clark Kent, Rachel Brosnahan (‚ÄúThe Marvelous Mrs. Maisel‚Äù) as Lois Lane and Nicholas Hoult (the ‚ÄúX-Men‚Äù movies, ‚ÄúJuror #2‚Äù) as Lex Luthor.  The film also stars Edi Gathegi (‚ÄúFor All Mankind‚Äù), Anthony Carrigan (‚ÄúBarry,‚Äù ‚ÄúGotham‚Äù), Nathan Fillion (the ‚ÄúGuardians of the Galaxy‚Äù films, ‚ÄúThe Suicide Squad‚Äù), Isabela Merced (‚ÄúAlien Romulus‚Äù), Skyler Gisondo (‚ÄúLicorice Pizza,‚Äù ‚ÄúBooksmart‚Äù), Sara Sampaio (‚ÄúAt Midnight‚Äù), Mar√≠a Gabriela de Far√≠a (‚ÄúThe Moodys‚Äù), Wendell Pierce (‚ÄúSelma,‚Äù ‚ÄúTom Clancy‚Äôs Jack Ryan‚Äù), Alan Tudyk (‚ÄúAndor‚Äù), Pruitt Taylor Vince (‚ÄúBird Box‚Äù) and Neva Howell (‚ÄúGreedy People‚Äù).

‚ÄúSuperman‚Äù is executive produced by Nikolas Korda, Chantal Nong Vo and Lars Winther.  Behind the camera, Gunn is joined by frequent collaborators, including director of photography Henry Braham, production designer Beth Mickle, costume designer Judianna Makovsky and composer John Murphy, along with editors William Hoy (‚ÄúThe Batman‚Äù), Jason Ballantine (the ‚ÄúIT‚Äù films, ‚ÄúThe Flash‚Äù) and Craig Alpert (‚ÄúDeadpool 2,‚Äù ‚ÄúBlue Beetle‚Äù).

‚ÄúSuperman‚Äù will be in theaters and IMAX nationwide on July 11, 2025, and internationally beginning 9 July 2025, distributed by Warner Bros. Pictures.

Aas Paas Last Mega Episode Part - 01 - [Eng Sub] - Laiba Khan - Ali Ansari - 2nd April 2025 - HAR PAL GEO

Aas Paas is a story of love, sacrifice, and the struggles within the relationships we often take for granted.
Arshia, a strong-willed young woman, is determined to reunite her broken family after her father abandons them. Meanwhile, Dr. Saham, a dedicated professional carrying his own burdens,
crosses paths with her.
Bound by their selflessness, they embark on a journey where their devotion to family is tested, and their own happiness is put on the line.
Will Arshia succeed in bringing her family back together? What challenges await Dr. Saham and Arshia? Could love blossom between them?

Lyrics:
Namo Namo Durge Sukh Karni
Namo Namo Ambe Dukh Harni
Nirakar Hai Jyoti Tumhari
Tihun Lok Phaili Ujiyari

Shashi Lalaat Mukh Maha Vishala
Netra Lal Bhrikouti Vikarala
Roop Maatu Ko Adhik Suhave
Darsh Karat Jan Ati Sukh Paave
Tum Sansar Shakti Ley Keena
Palan Hetu Anna Dhan Deena
Annapoorna Hui Jag Paala
Tumhi Aadi Sundari Bala

Pralayakal Sab Nashaan Haari
Tum Gouri Shiv Shankar Pyari
Shiv Yogi Tumhare Gun Gaavein
Brahma Vishnu Tumhein Nit Dhyaave
Roop Saraswati Ko Tum Dhara
De Subuddhi Rishi Munina Ubara
Dhara Roop Narsimha Ko Amba
Pragat Bhayi Phaad Kar Khamba

Raksha Kari Prahlad Bachayo
Hiranyaykush Ko Swarg Pathayo
Lakshmi Roop Dharo Jag Mahin
Shree Narayan Anga Samahin

Ksheer Sindhu Mein Karat Vilaasa
Daya Sindhu Deejey Mann Aasa
Hingalaja Mein Tumhi Bhawani
Mahima Amit Na Jaat Bakhani

Matangi Dhoomawati Mata
Bhuvaneshwari Bagala Sukhdata
Shree Bhairav Tara Jag Tarini
Chhinna Bhala Bhava Dukh Nivarini
Kehari Vahan Sohe Bhawani
Laangur Veer Chalat Agavani
Kar Mein Khappar Khadaga Virajay
Jako Dekh Kaal Darr Bhajey

Sohe Astra Aur Trishula
Jate Uthata Shatru Hiya Shoola

Nagkoti Mein Toumhi Virajat
Tihoun Lok Mein Danka Baajat
Shumbh Nishumbh Daanav Tum Maare
Rakta Beej Shankhana Sanghaare
Mahishasur Nrip Ati Abhimani
Jehi Agh Bhar Mahi Akulaani

Roop Karaal Kali Ka Dhara
Sena Sahita Tum Tihin Samhara
Pidh Pari Santana Par Jab Jab
Bhayi Sahay Maat Tum Tab Tab
Amarpuri Auro Sab Lokaa
Tab Mahima Sab Rahey Ashoka
Jwala Mein Hai Jyoti Tumhari
Tumhein Sada Poojey Nar Nari

Prem Bhakti Se Jo Jas Gaave
Dukh Daridra Nikat Nahin Aave
Dhyave Jo Nar Man Layi
Janma Maran Tako Chhouti Jaayi
Jogi Sur Muni Kahat Pukaari
Yog Nahi Bina Shakti Tumhari
Shankar Acharaj Tap Kinho
Kaamaru Krodh Jeet Sab Leenho

Nishdin Dhyan Dharo Shankar Ko
Kaahu Kaal Nahin Sumiro Tumko
Shakti Roop Ko Maram Na Paayo
Shakti Gayi Tab Mann Pachitayo
Sharnagat Huyi Kiriti Bakhai
Jai Jai Jai Jagadambe Bhawani

Bhayi Prasanna Aadi Jagadamba
Dayi Shakti Nahin Keen Vilamba

Maukon Maatu Kashta Ati Ghero
Tum Bin Kaun Hare Dukh Mero
Asha Trishna Nipat Satave
Ripu Murakh Mohi Ati Darpave
Shatru Nash Keejai Maharani
Soumiron Ikchit Tumhein Bhawani
Karo Kripa Hey Maatu Dayala
Riddhi Siddhi Dey Karahou Nihaala

Jab Lagi Jiyoun Daya Phal Paun
Tumharo Jas Mein Sada Sunaun
Durga Chalisa Jo Koi Gaavey
Sab Sukh Bhog Parampad Paave

Devidas Sharan Neej Jaani
Karahun Krupa Jagadambe Bhawani
Karahun Krupa Jagadambe Bhawani

Sharanagat Raksha Kare
Bhakt Rahe Nishank
Me Aaya Teri Sharan Mein

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal‚Äôs Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

Click here to watch more episodes from 'Jetha Aur Bhide Ki Nok Jhonk' : https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLSXTaG1fT0cTAUo34hpXVbh1keqAyhuhj

snippet.description:

Aas Paas Last Mega Episode Part - 02 - [Eng Sub] - Laiba Khan - Ali Ansari - 2nd April 2025 - HAR PAL GEO

Aas Paas is a story of love, sacrifice, and the struggles within the relationships we often take for granted.
Arshia, a strong-willed young woman, is determined to reunite her broken family after her father abandons them. Meanwhile, Dr. Saham, a dedicated professional carrying his own burdens,
crosses paths with her.
Bound by their selflessness, they embark on a journey where their devotion to family is tested, and their own happiness is put on the line.
Will Arshia succeed in bringing her family back together? What challenges await Dr. Saham and Arshia? Could love blossom between them?

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Director: Muhammad Iftikhar Iffi
Writer: Samra Bukhari

snippet.title: M3GAN 2.0 Official Trailer
snippet.description:
oops! she did it again!
#M3GAN2 is only in theaters June 27. 

---
Website: http://www.M3GANmovie.com
YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/universalpictures  
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/meetM3GAN/
X: https://twitter.com/meetm3gan
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/M3GAN/
TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/m3gan


The murderous doll who captivated pop culture in 2023 is back. And this time she‚Äôs not alone. 

The original creative team behind that phenomenon‚Äîled by horror titans James Wan for Atomic Monster, Jason Blum for Blumhouse and writer-director Gerard Johnstone‚Äîreboot an all-new wild chapter in A.I. mayhem with M3GAN 2.0. Two years after M3GAN, a marvel of artificial intelligence, went rogue and embarked on
a murderous (and impeccably choreographed) rampage and was subsequently
destroyed, M3GAN‚Äôs creator Gemma (Allison Williams) has become a high-profile author and advocate for government oversight of A.I. Meanwhile, Gemma‚Äôs niece Cady (Violet McGraw), now 14, has become a teenager, rebelling against Gemma‚Äôs overprotective rules.

Unbeknownst to them, the underlying tech for M3GAN has been stolen and misused by a powerful defense contractor to create a military-grade weapon known as Amelia (Ivanna Sakhno; Ahsoka, Pacific Rim: Uprising), the ultimate killer infiltration spy. But as Amelia‚Äôs self-awareness increases, she becomes decidedly less interested in taking orders from humans. Or in keeping them around. 

With the future of human existence on the line, Gemma realizes that the only option is to resurrect M3GAN (Amie Donald, voiced by Jenna Davis) and give her a few upgrades, making her faster, stronger, and more lethal. As their paths collide, the original A.I icon is about to meet her match.

M3GAN 2.0 is written and directed by acclaimed returning filmmaker Gerard Johnstone, from a story by Gerard Johnstone and Akela Cooper, based on characters created by Akela Cooper & James Wan.

The film co-stars returning cast members Brian Jordan Alvarez and Jen Van Epps as Gemma‚Äôs loyal tech teammates, Cole and Tess, and new characters played by Aristotle Athari (Saturday Night Live, Hacks), Timm Sharp (Apples Never Fall, Percy Jackson and the Olympians) and Grammy winner and 11-time Emmy nominee Jemaine Clement (Avatar: The Way of Water, What We Do in the Shadows). 

Produced by James Wan, Jason Blum and Allison Williams, the film is executive produced by Gerard Johnstone, Adam Hendricks, Greg Gilreath, Michael Clear, Judson Scott and Mark D. Katchur. 

The first M3GAN film shattered box office records, opening to $30.4 million domestically to become the biggest opening weekend for a PG-13 horror film since A Quiet Place Part II. The film went on to gross more than $180 million worldwide.

This is the story of Khushboo Patani, a former Major in the Indian Army, who retired after years of dedicated service. She has shared her journey, filled with struggles and challenges, which shaped her into a person full of confidence and courage.

Her journey began in Bareilly, where she excelled in education with the support of her parents. She speaks about overcoming fear and self-doubt, and how she moved forward with determination. Throughout her experiences, she has addressed important issues like mental health, bullying, and self-respect. She shares how she faced hardships in life and ultimately decided to join the Indian Army. According to her, the more challenges we face, the stronger we become.

During her service in the Indian Army, she not only pushed her own limits but also worked towards helping others, maintaining peace, and resolving conflicts. Her experiences taught her that as long as our inner strength remains intact, no obstacle can defeat us.

Her story carries a powerful message‚Äîwe are never victims, but warriors fighting the battles of life. She also shared how she participated in peacekeeping missions and made efforts to help those in need.
In the end, Khushboo Patani encourages young people to trust their inner voice and take bold steps to bring positive change in life. Her story is not only deeply inspiring but also highlights the importance of mental health and resilience.

This is the story of Khushboo Patani, a former Major in the Indian Army, who retired after years of dedicated service. She has shared her journey, filled with struggles and challenges, which shaped her into a person full of confidence and courage.

Her journey began in Bareilly, where she excelled in education with the support of her parents. She speaks about overcoming fear and self-doubt, and how she moved forward with determination. Throughout her experiences, she has addressed important issues like mental health, bullying, and self-respect. She shares how she faced hardships in life and ultimately decided to join the Indian Army. According to her, the more challenges we face, the stronger we become.

During her service in the Indian Army, she not only pushed her own limits but also worked towards helping others, maintaining peace, and resolving conflicts. Her experiences taught her that as long as our inner strength remains intact, no obstacle can defeat us.

Her story carries a powerful message‚Äîwe are never victims, but warriors fighting the battles of life. She also shared how she participated in peacekeeping missions and made efforts to help those in need.
In the end, Khushboo Patani encourages young people to trust their inner voice and take bold steps to bring positive change in life. Her story is not only deeply inspiring but also highlights the importance of mental health and resilience.

Karate Kid: Legends unites the iconic martial arts masters of one of the most beloved film franchises of all time to tell a completely new story full of action and heart.‚ÄØWhen kung fu prodigy Li Fong (Ben Wang) relocates to New York City with his mother to attend a prestigious new school, he finds solace in a new friendship with a classmate and her father. But his newfound peace is short-lived after he attracts unwanted attention from a formidable local karate champion. Driven by a desire to defend himself, Li embarks on a journey to enter the ultimate karate competition. Guided by the wisdom of his kung fu teacher, Mr. Han (Jackie Chan), and the legendary Karate Kid, Daniel LaRusso (Ralph Macchio), Li merges their unique styles to prepare for an epic martial arts showdown.

Written by: Rob Lieber    

Produced by: Karen Rosenfelt

snippet.description:
Sandeep Maheshwari is a name among millions who struggled, failed and surged ahead in search of success, happiness and contentment. snippet.title: Pm Awas Yojana Gramin apply online 2025 | Pradhanmantri Awas Yojana 2025 online | Awas Yojana Gramin
snippet.description:
Pm Awas Yojana Gramin apply online 2025 | Pradhanmantri Awas Yojana 2025 online | Awas Yojana Gramin
This Video Is about Pm Awas Yojana Gramin apply online 2025.Here is good news for rural families! The Government has announced that you can now apply online for the PM Awas Yojana Gramin (PMAY-G). This housing scheme aims to provide affordable homes to families living in rural areas. In this video, we will guide you through the step-by-step process of applying for PMAY Gramin online in 2024. Learn how to fill out the application form, check eligibility, and complete the process with ease. Don't miss out on this amazing opportunity to secure a home under the government's housing initiative. Watch now to know more!"

snippet.title: Sikandar Movie REVIEW | Deeksha Sharma
snippet.description:
Sikandar Salman Khan Comeback Movie Directed by AR Murugadoss with Rashmika Mandanna is totally wasted opportunity with Old Mass & Funny Emotions combined with Slow Salman Khan Action & Bigger than life poor presentation.

Sikandar Full Movie Review By Deeksha Sharma with Positives & Negatives would be shared in this Video. Bollywood Biggest Fanbase Star Salman Khan actually tried his best or Another chance would be needed for Much Awaited Comeback? Find Clear answer inside!

Sikandar is a 2025 Indian Hindi-language action thriller film directed by A. R. Murugadoss and produced by Sajid Nadiadwala. The film stars Salman Khan in the titular role, alongside Rashmika Mandanna, Sathyaraj, Kajal Aggarwal, Sharman Joshi, Prateik Babbar, Kishore, Jatin Sarna and Sanjay Kapoor. In the film, Sanjay "Sikandar" Rajkot, the king of Rajkot, becomes a target for Minister Rakesh Pradhan after killing his son. When his wife‚Äôs donated organs save three lives, Rakesh seeks revenge, forcing Sanjay to protect them.

The film was officially announced in April 2024. Principal photography commenced the following June in Mumbai and wrapped by March 2025. The film has songs composed by Pritam, background score composed by Santhosh Narayanan, cinematography handled by Tirru and editing by Vivek Harshan. With an estimated production budget of ‚Çπ200 crore, it is one of the most expensive Indian films of all time.

Sikandar was theatrically released worldwide on 30 March 2025, in standard and IMAX formats, coinciding with Eid al-Fitr.

Aas Paas 2nd Last Episode 31 - [Eng Sub] - Laiba Khan - Ali Ansari - 1st April 2025 - HAR PAL GEO

Aas Paas is a story of love, sacrifice, and the struggles within the relationships we often take for granted.
Arshia, a strong-willed young woman, is determined to reunite her broken family after her father abandons them. Meanwhile, Dr. Saham, a dedicated professional carrying his own burdens,
crosses paths with her.
Bound by their selflessness, they embark on a journey where their devotion to family is tested, and their own happiness is put on the line.
Will Arshia succeed in bringing her family back together? What challenges await Dr. Saham and Arshia? Could love blossom between them?

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. snippet.title: The Bhootnii (Official Trailer) | Sanjay D, Mouni R, Sunny S, Palak T, Nick | Sidhaant S | Deepak M
snippet.description:
Get ready for a spooky, hilarious, and mind-bending ride with The Bhootnii üëªüé¨ This horror-comedy-sci-fi adventure brings together the best of chills and laughs, starring Sanjay Dutt as the fearless Ghostbuster Baba, who must face the ultimate paranormal challenge: Mouni Roy as a powerful and mysterious ghost.

Joining this epic journey are Sunny Singh, Palak Tiwari, Aasif Khan and Beyounick, bringing their comedic chops and unforgettable performances to the screen. With Baba and his team on a mission to stop the ghostly forces, prepare for a rollercoaster of supernatural thrills and gut-busting moments.

Will Baba and his quirky team defeat Bhootnii or will the ghost take over?

The Bhootnii hits theaters on 18th April 2025!

snippet.description:
Real Madrid booked their place in the final of the Copa del Rey and on 26 April they will battle it out against Barcelona or Atl√©tico at La Cartuja stadium (Seville) for the trophy. The match was decided in extra-time, following a nail-biting end to the game. Barrenetxea gave Real Sociedad the lead after 16 minutes and Endrick made it 1-1 in the 30th minute after an exquisite assist from Vini Jr. with the outside of his right foot. In the second half, two Alaba own goals made it 1-3 in the 80th minute, but from 82‚Äò to 86‚Äô Madrid rampaged and Bellingham, after another precise assist from Vini Jr, and Tchouameni brought the score to 3-3. In the 93rd minute, Oyarzabal took the game into extra-time, where the Whites sealed their semi-final berth in the 115th minute when R√ºdiger headed home G√ºler's corner.
